            "text": "<p><strong>How To Use</strong></p><p>Cleanse and dry your skin. Use your Q-Rejuvalight Pro on Skin Clearing Mode for a full 3-minute session. Follow with a refreshing spritz of the Dermal Mist to soothe and lock in moisture.</p>",
